Note:
Runa Standard Library: Blockchain Governance Voting Module

Provides comprehensive voting mechanisms and strategies for blockchain governance systems.
Implements enterprise-grade voting protocols including multiple voting methods, ballot
systems, vote aggregation, and result calculation. Competitive with production voting
implementations in Ethereum governance, Cosmos SDK voting, and other leading blockchain
governance platforms.

Features:
- Multiple voting strategies and ballot types
- Ranked choice voting and instant runoff systems
- Weighted voting with stake-based power calculation
- Anonymous voting with zero-knowledge proofs
- Quadratic voting and quadratic funding mechanisms
- Liquid democracy with delegation chains
- Vote splitting and partial voting support
- Time-based voting windows and snapshot voting
- Vote verification and audit trails
- Sybil resistance and vote buying protection
- Real-time vote counting and result calculation
- Vote privacy and secret ballot mechanisms
- Slashing for malicious voting behavior
- Cross-chain voting coordination
- Governance token integration and rewards
:End Note

Note: Core Voting Types
Type called "VotingEngine":
    voting_strategies as Dictionary[String, VotingStrategy]
    ballot_manager as BallotManager
    vote_aggregator as VoteAggregator
    snapshot_manager as SnapshotManager
    delegation_engine as DelegationEngine
    privacy_manager as PrivacyManager
    verification_system as VerificationSystem
    rewards_calculator as RewardsCalculator
    anti_sybil_system as AntiSybilSystem

Type called "VotingStrategy":
    strategy_name as String
    strategy_type as StrategyType
    configuration as StrategyConfiguration
    validator as StrategyValidator
    calculator as ResultCalculator

Type StrategyType is:
    | SIMPLE_MAJORITY
    | WEIGHTED_MAJORITY
    | RANKED_CHOICE
    | QUADRATIC_VOTING
    | APPROVAL_VOTING
    | LIQUID_DEMOCRACY
    | CONVICTION_VOTING
    | FUTARCHY
    | HOLOGRAPHIC_CONSENSUS

Type called "BallotManager":
    active_ballots as Dictionary[String, Ballot]
    ballot_templates as Dictionary[String, BallotTemplate]
    voting_sessions as Dictionary[String, VotingSession]
    ballot_history as Dictionary[String, List[Ballot]]

Type called "Ballot":
    ballot_id as String
    proposal_id as String
    ballot_type as BallotType
    options as List[VotingOption]
    voting_period as VotingPeriod
    eligibility_criteria as EligibilityCriteria
    voting_parameters as VotingParameters
    results as BallotResults
    status as BallotStatus

Type BallotType is:
    | SINGLE_CHOICE
    | MULTIPLE_CHOICE
    | RANKED_CHOICE
    | WEIGHTED_CHOICE
    | APPROVAL_BALLOT
    | SCORED_BALLOT

Type called "VotingOption":
    option_id as String
    option_text as String
    option_data as Dictionary[String, Any]
    vote_count as Integer
    weighted_votes as Float
    supporters as List[String]

Type called "VotingPeriod":
    start_block as Integer
